  "text": "In addition, real time systems that belongs to information either feed by users or nonhumans sensors needed high level of response which in turns demand high level computing resources, such as GPS system, mobile embedded sensor's data processing etc. Such systems are costly in terms of energy and they cause limiting the mobile phone in providing the reliable services. Furthermore, the emerging of high computational intensive applications [CITATION_1] i.e. speech recognizers, natural language translators, online video games, and wearable sensor devices etc., in the mobile computing environment increased the user's expectations, while they need a high computing power, battery lifetime and storage memory in the resource constrained devices (SIDs).",
